    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778516>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A, Puparium of aphidophagous syrphid in Baltic amber (Diptera: Syrphidae: Syrphinae) (KAM No. 6361) with an emergence hole typical for Diplazontinae, ventral view. B, Right lateral view; Emergence holes of various recent parasitoids of aphidophagous syrphids (Diptera, Syrphidae, Syrphinae). C, Diplazon pectoratorius. D, Syrphoctonus sp. E and F, Diplazon laetatorius. G, Cryptinae (gen. et sp. indet). H, Asaphes sp. (Pteromalidae). Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778516/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

